title: F-35 rules the skies at UK airshow
text:
F-35 rules the skies at UK airshow 4:17pm GMT - 01:23 
Defence spending took centre stage at Britain's Farnborough airshow, but it wasn't hard to guess the star of the show once the new F-35 took to the skies. ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
